Product Description

5FT Flat Plug Power Strip Surge protector with USB

8 AC outlet cord with 6 USB(1 USB-C) ports for home and office

8 AC power sockets are designed to be wider, so the power adapters will not interfere with each otherIdeal for multiple devices charge together, whether as a desktop power strip or a nightstand charging station, it can be competent

6 USB ports ( Total 5V/3.4A 17W) . USB A ports can charge up to 2.4A , and the USB C port can charge up to 3A. would assign ideal current intelligently for your phone or tablets

Specification:

  • Rated Power: 1250W MAX
  • Input:100-240V 10A 50/60HZ
  • USB Output: 5V/3.4A 17W
  • Cord Length:5ft
  • Dimension:6.6*4*1.1in
  • USB -A Output:5V/2.4A Max
  • USB -C Output:5V/3A Max

Wide-spaced AC power outlets

8 widely spaced AC power sockets can accommodate large adapters without blocking each other, and 6 USB sockets for a total of 14 devices. Keep your desktop clean and beautiful without additional converters

Wall Mount Power Strip

Mount this USB power outlet on the wall, bench, wall mount, under the counter wherever you want via the 2 slots on the back

Overload Protection

When the load power exceeds 1250W, cut off the overload switch in time to prevent short-circuit fire, and cut off the power supply in time when danger occurs, effectively avoiding the risk of accidental fire and short-circuit. After troubleshooting, press the switch to resume normal use

45 flat plug

Flat plug with only 0.35 inch ultra slim design,can be installed in tight spots behind furniture such as beds, bedside tables, sofas or TVs. The 45 degree angle design will not block the bottom socket of the wall socket. It is the ultimate space saving power strip for your home, office

Anti-slip design

6 high-strength non-slip silicone pads are embedded in the base of the product to prevent the socket from accidentally slipping

6 USB Charging Ports

The USB C power strip has 6 USB ports which charge up to 17WNote: The UCB C port is not Quick Charger 3.0

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
